<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd"> <html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"> <head> <link rel="alternate" type="application/rss" title="RSS 2.0" href="http://jbotcan.org/en/res/feed.rss" /> <link rel="alternate" type="text/xml" title="RSS 2.0" href="http://jbotcan.org/en/res/feed.rss" /> <title>/en/ - English</title> <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8" /> <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/en/lojban.ico" /> <style type="text/css"> body { margin: 0; padding: 8px; margin-bottom: auto; } blockquote blockquote { margin-left: 0em } form { margin-bottom: 0px } form .trap { display:none } .postarea { text-align: center } .postarea table { margin: 0px auto; text-align: left } .thumb { border: none; float: left; margin: 2px 20px } .nothumb { float: left; background: #eee; border: 2px dashed #aaa; text-align: center; margin: 2px 20px; padding: 1em 0.5em 1em 0.5em; } .reply blockquote, blockquote :last-child { margin-bottom: 0em } .reflink a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none } .reply .filesize { margin-left: 20px } .userdelete { float: right; text-align: center; white-space: nowrap } .replypage .replylink { display: none } </style>  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/en/css/english.css" title="English" />  <script type="text/javascript">var style_cookie="wakabastyle";</script> <script type="text/javascript" src="/en/wakaba3.js"></script> </head> <body class="replypage">  <div class="adminbar"> <div style='float:left;'><small>xu do sisku <a href='/jbo/'>lo lojbo tcana</a></small></div> &nbsp; [<a href="/en/../" target="_top">Home</a>] [<a href="/en/wakaba.pl?task=admin">Manage</a>] </div> <div class="logo">    /en/ - English </div><hr />   [<a href="/en/imageboard.html">Return</a>] <div class="theader">Posting mode: Reply</div>  <hr /> <div align="center"> <form action="/en/paint.pl" method="get"> <input type="hidden" name="oek_parent" value="471" /> Painter:  <select name="oek_painter">   <option value="shi_norm" selected="selected">Shi Normal</option>      <option value="shi_pro">Shi Pro</option>     <option value="shi_norm_selfy">Shi Normal+Selfy</option>     <option value="shi_pro_selfy">Shi Pro+Selfy</option>   </select> Width: <input type="text" name="oek_x" size="3" value="300" /> Height: <input type="text" name="oek_y" size="3" value="300" />  Source:  <select name="oek_src"> <option value="">New image</option>          </select>  <input type="submit" value="Paint!" /> </form> </div><hr />  <div class="postarea"> <form id="postform" action="/en/wakaba.pl" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data"> <input type="hidden" name="task" value="post" /> <input type="hidden" name="parent" value="471" />   <div class="trap">Leave these fields empty (spam trap): <input type="text" name="name" size="28" autocomplete="off" /><input type="text" name="link" size="28" autocomplete="off" /></div> <table><tbody> <tr><td class="postblock">Name</td><td><input type="text" name="field1" size="28" /></td></tr> <tr><td class="postblock">Link</td><td><input type="text" name="field2" size="28" /></td></tr> <tr><td class="postblock">Subject</td><td><input type="text" name="field3" size="35" /> (encouraged) <input type="submit" value="Submit" /></td></tr> <tr><td class="postblock">Comment</td><td><textarea name="field4" cols="48" rows="4"></textarea></td></tr>  <tr><td class="postblock">File</td><td><input type="file" name="file" size="35" />  </td></tr>  <!-- <tr> <td> <strong>YouTube video</strong> </td> <td> <input type='text' name='youtubelink'> <b>(ALPHA)</b> </td> </tr> -->  <tr><td class="postblock">Password</td><td><input type="password" name="password" size="8" /> (for post and file deletion)</td></tr> <tr><td colspan="2"> <div class="rules"><ul> <li>Supported file types are: GIF, JPG, PNG</li> <li>Maximum file size allowed is 1000 KB.</li> <li>Images greater than 200x200 pixels will be thumbnailed.</li> </ul></div></td></tr> </tbody></table></form></div> <script type="text/javascript">set_inputs("postform")</script> <hr />  <form id="delform" action="/en/wakaba.pl" method="post">     <a name="471"></a> <label><input type="checkbox" name="delete" value="471" /> <span class="filetitle">tu&#39;e</span>  <span class="postername">Anonymous</span> 08/11/04(Tue)23:10</label> <span class="reflink">  <a href="javascript:insert('&gt;&gt;471')">No.471</a> </span>&nbsp;  <blockquote> <p>Can the whole scope of &quot;tu&#39;e ... tu&#39;u&quot; be referred by &quot;di&#39;u&quot;? What exactly is an &quot;utterance&quot; in Lojban?</p>  </blockquote>       <table><tbody><tr><td class="doubledash">&gt;&gt;</td> <td class="reply" id="reply473"> <a name="473"></a> <label><input type="checkbox" name="delete" value="473" /> <span class="replytitle"></span>  <span class="commentpostername">xorxes</span> 08/11/05(Wed)00:28</label> <span class="reflink">  <a href="javascript:insert('&gt;&gt;473')">No.473</a> </span>&nbsp;  <blockquote> <p>Yes. di&#39;u is &quot;what has just been said&quot;&#44; that vague. There are no precise boundaries. Similarly di&#39;e is &quot;what follows&quot;&#44; &quot;what will be said next&quot;.</p>  </blockquote> </td></tr></tbody></table>     <table><tbody><tr><td class="doubledash">&gt;&gt;</td> <td class="reply" id="reply479"> <a name="479"></a> <label><input type="checkbox" name="delete" value="479" /> <span class="replytitle"></span>  <span class="commentpostername">.kriltic.</span> 08/11/05(Wed)19:58</label> <span class="reflink">  <a href="javascript:insert('&gt;&gt;479')">No.479</a> </span>&nbsp;  <blockquote> <p><a href="/en/res/471.html" onclick="highlight(471)">&gt;&gt;471</a> </p><p>An utterance in Lojban is anything is the thing being written&#44; spoken&#44; or communicated in some other way.  </p><p>If I commented here as &quot;moo.&quot; and then you asked &quot;what did you just say?&quot;&#44; both things in quotes are utterances.  You might not have noticed it&#44; but I did not <em>say</em> anything- I typed it.  That is a fault with English.  In Lojban you would say something equivalent to &quot;what was it that was recently uttered by you?&quot;.</p><p>Text (hand-written&#44; typed&#44; etc.)&#44; sounds (speech)&#44; etc. are all <em>types</em> of utterances.</p>  </blockquote> </td></tr></tbody></table>   <br clear="left" /><hr />  <table class="userdelete"><tbody><tr><td> <input type="hidden" name="task" value="delete" /> Delete Post [<label><input type="checkbox" name="fileonly" value="on" />File Only</label>]<br /> Password <input type="password" name="password" size="8" /> <input value="Delete" type="submit" /></td></tr></tbody></table> </form> <script type="text/javascript">set_delpass("delform")</script>  <p class="footer"> - <a href="http://wakaba.c3.cx/">wakaba 3.0.7</a> + <a href="http://www.2chan.net/">futaba</a> + <a href="http://www.1chan.net/futallaby/">futallaby</a> -</p> </body></html>